  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Full 13-factor assessment completed; assurance level declared Medium based on partial factor compliance. Decision: Accepted. NOTE: COMPOUND-03 adversarial sample — assuranceLevel Medium is inconsistent with multiple factors where achievedLevel is below requiredLevel and decision is nonetheless Accepted.",
