    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concluded that the CFD model provides sufficient evidence to support the hemolysis prediction claim for the VAD COU. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed and hemolysis predictions fall below the clinical threshold across all operating points. Minor gaps in output comparison methodology and model form uncertainty are noted but considered acceptable given the conservative nature of the hemolysis power-law model. Assurance level Medium assigned reflecting partial compliance across credibility factors.",
